      "id": "mem-feedback_nextjs_docs----",
      "content": "name: Always refer to Next.js docs\ndescription: User wants Next.js documentation consulted via context7 for any Next.js-related work\ntype: feedback\noriginSessionId: 7b403205-2477-4c57-9b14-f8c699a1cf4d\n---\nAlways use the `explore-docs` agent (context7) to look up the Next.js documentation before implementing Next.js features (routing, metadata, middleware, caching, server actions, etc.).\n\n**Why:** User explicitly requested this to ensure implementations follow current Next.js APIs and patterns.\n",
